data.description: Discover the ultimate riverfront lifestyle with this exceptional property nestled along the picturesque Middle Ford of the Willamette River. Offering unobstructed views that extend endlessly, and the luxury of fishing from your own backyard, this home presents an unparalleled opportunity for waterfront living.With three bedrooms, two full baths, and a versatile flex space, the residence exudes potential. Abundant natural light bathes the interior spaces, creating an inviting ambiance that seamlessly merges with the stunning river panorama visible from your back porch.Nestled on just under half an acre, the home enjoys privacy as it rests towards the rear of the property. A two-car garage and an outbuilding cater to storage needs while enhancing the property's functionality.Included are the appliances showcased in the images, with the exception of the washer and dryer. Imagine waking up to the soothing sounds of the river, spending leisurely days skiing nearby slopes, hiking scenic trails, and casting your line in pursuit of the day's catch?all easily accessible.For aquatic enthusiasts, a nearby lake further amplifies the appeal of this location. Beyond being a residence, this property epitomizes the opportunity to claim your personal haven within Oregon's embrace. Set within the quaint town of Oakridge, you'll discover solace, excitement, and the essence of riverfront living at its finest.This is your moment to seize the chance of owning a slice of paradise?come and explore the facets of this riverfront gem in the serene embrace of Oakridge, Oregon. Your gateway to an idyllic waterfront lifestyle awaits.
